<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q1_v14" title="Operaciones con enteros" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Considera la siguiente expresión:</p>
    <p>
      <m:math>
        <m:mrow>
          <m:mn>1</m:mn>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
          <m:mo>(</m:mo>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mo>−</m:mo>
          <m:mn>9</m:mn>
          <m:mo>)</m:mo>
        </m:mrow>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes igualdades es verdadera?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>66</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al resolver primero el segundo paréntesis se obtiene −13. Luego, (−5)(−13) = 65 y finalmente 1 − 65 = −64. Por lo tanto, la igualdad con 66 no es verdadera.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>64</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Se calcula primero −4 − 9 = −13. Después, (−5)(−13) = 65. Finalmente, 1 − 65 = −64. Por eso esta igualdad es verdadera.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>78</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El valor de la expresión es 1 − (−5)(−13) = 1 − 65 = −64. Como −64 ≠ −78, esa igualdad no es verdadera.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>5</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>(</m:mo>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
            <m:mo>−</m:mo>
            <m:mn>9</m:mn>
            <m:mo>)</m:mo>
            <m:mo>=</m:mo>
            <m:mn>26</m:mn>
          </m:mrow>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Al desarrollar la expresión se obtiene −4 − 9 = −13, luego (−5)(−13) = 65 y por último 1 − 65 = −64. Entonces no puede ser igual a 26.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Resolver el segundo paréntesis</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>13</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reemplazar en la expresión original</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>13</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Multiplicar los dos números negativos</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>13</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>65</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
            <p>El producto de dos números negativos es positivo.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Restar el resultado obtenido</strong></p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>65</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>64</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La igualdad verdadera es la alternativa B.</p>
            <p>
              <m:math>
                <m:mrow>
                  <m:mn>1</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>5</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>4</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>9</m:mn>
                  <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                  <m:mo>−</m:mo>
                  <m:mn>64</m:mn>
                </m:mrow>
              </m:math>
            </p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>